actionCellButton.customFunction: let $injector = widgetContext.$scope.$injector; let customDialog = $injector.get(widgetContext.servicesMap.get('customDialog')), deviceService = $injector.get(widgetContext.servicesMap.get('deviceService')), entityRelationService = $injector.get(widgetContext.servicesMap.get('entityRelationService')), entityGroupService = $injector.get(widgetContext.servicesMap.get('entityGroupService')); entityService = $injector.get(widgetContext.servicesMap.get('entityService')); // userPermissionsService = $injector.get(widgetContext.servicesMap.get('userPermissionsService')); openEditDeviceDialog(); function openEditDeviceDialog() { customDialog.customDialog(htmlTemplate, EditDeviceDialogController).subscribe(); } function EditDeviceDialogController(instance) { let vm = instance; vm.device = {}; vm.editDeviceFormGroup = vm.fb.group({ deviceName: ['', [vm.validators.required]], deviceLabel: [null], targetOwner: [null, [vm.validators.required]] }); init().subscribe(() => { getEntityInfo(); }); vm.cancel = function() { vm.dialogRef.close(null); }; vm.save = () => { vm.loading = true; vm.editDeviceFormGroup.markAsPristine(); saveDevice().subscribe( (/*device*/) => { changeDeviceOwner().subscribe( () => { vm.loading = false; widgetContext.updateAliases(); vm.dialogRef.close(null); }, () => { vm.loading = false; } ); }, () => { vm.loading = false; } ); }; function init() { vm.availableOwners = [ { name: 'Tenant', id: {id: widgetContext.currentUser.tenantId, entityType: 'TENANT' } } ]; return getEntityGroupByName('Andaman Draft', 'CUSTOMER').pipe( widgetContext.rxjs.switchMap((Andaman Draft) => { if (Andaman Draft) { var query = { entityFilter: { type: 'entityGroup', groupType: 'CUSTOMER', entityGroup: AndamanDraft.id.id }, pageLink: { pageSize: 100, page: 0 }, entityFields: [ { key: 'name', type: 'ENTITY_FIELD' } ] }; return entityService.findEntityDataByQuery(query).pipe( widgetContext.rxjs.switchMap((data) => { const availableCustomers = data.data.map((entityData) => { return { id: entityData.entityId, name: entityData.latest["ENTITY_FIELD"].name.value }; }); vm.availableOwners = vm.availableOwners.concat(availableCustomers); return widgetContext.rxjs.of(null); }) ); } else { return widgetContext.rxjs.of(null); } } )); } function getEntityInfo() { vm.loading = true; deviceService.getDevice(entityId.id).subscribe( (device) => { vm.device = device; let ownerId = vm.device.ownerId; let targetOwner = vm.availableOwners.find((owner) => owner.id.id === ownerId.id); vm.editDeviceFormGroup.patchValue({ deviceName: vm.device.name, deviceLabel: vm.device.label, targetOwner: targetOwner }, {emitEvent: false}); vm.loading = false; } ); } function saveDevice() { const formValues = vm.editDeviceFormGroup.value; if (vm.device.name !== formValues.deviceName || (vm.device.label !== formValues.deviceLabel)) { vm.device.name = formValues.deviceName; vm.device.label = formValues.deviceLabel; return deviceService.saveDevice(vm.device); } return widgetContext.rxjs.of([]); } function changeDeviceOwner() { let newOwner = vm.editDeviceFormGroup.get('targetOwner').value; if (newOwner.id !== vm.device.ownerId.id) { return widgetContext.rxjs.forkJoin([ entityGroupService.changeEntityOwner(newOwner.id, vm.device.id), saveRelations(vm.device.id, vm.device.ownerId, newOwner.id) ]); } return widgetContext.rxjs.of([]); } function saveRelations(deviceId, currentOwnerId, newOwnerId) { let tasks = [ deleteRelation(deviceId, currentOwnerId), addRelation(deviceId, newOwnerId) ]; return widgetContext.rxjs.forkJoin(tasks); } function addRelation(deviceId, targetOwnerId) { if (targetOwnerId.entityType === 'TENANT') { return widgetContext.rxjs.of(null); } else { let relation = { type: 'Owns', typeGroup: 'COMMON', from: targetOwnerId, to: deviceId }; return entityRelationService.saveRelation(relation); } } function deleteRelation(deviceId, currentOwnerId) { if (currentOwnerId.entityType === 'TENANT') { return widgetContext.rxjs.of(null); } else { let relation = { type: 'Owns', from: currentOwnerId, to: deviceId }; return entityRelationService.deleteRelation(relation.from, relation.type, relation.to); } } function getEntityGroupByName(groupName, groupType) { var entityGroupsPageLink = widgetContext.pageLink(10, 0, groupName); return entityGroupService.getEntityGroupsByPageLink(entityGroupsPageLink, groupType, {ignoreLoading: true}).pipe( widgetContext.rxjs.map((data) => { if (data.data.length) { return data.data.find((group) => group.name === groupName); } else { return null; } }) ); } }
